<B>__{mrs brown by jeremy brock}
<L>__{exterior the grounds of windsor castle, forest night}
<A>__{begin on black. the sound of rain driving into trees. something wipes frame and we are suddenly hurtling through a forest on the shoulders of a wild eyed, kilted john brown. drenched hair streaming, head swivelling left and right, as he searches the lightening dark. a crack to his left. he spins round, raises his pistol, smacks past saplings and plunges on.}
